@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.56) + wp.cos(wp.cos(v2 + 0.79)))
    v2 = 0.50
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.64) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.72)) * wp.sin((v2 + 0.25 + tmp + 0.44)))
    v2 = wp.cos((v0 * (v0 + 0.46 * v2 + 0.14)))
    v2 = (v2 / (v2 + wp.exp(v0 + 0.76)))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = (wp.exp(0.84) + (0.79 * 0.07))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
